title: PS3 ScummVM v1.50 RESIGNED pkg package
description:
ScummVM <a href=" http://scummvm.org/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://scummvm.org/</a>

Play a whole bunch of pointy-clicky adventure games on your homebrewed PS3! <a href=" http://scummvm.org/compatibility/1.5.0/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://scummvm.org/compatibility/1.5.0/</a>  GAMES NOT INCLUDED.

Of course this package won't work on OFW. You need a CFW firmware to install the package.

The original 1.5.0 package on ScummVM/SourceForge website is not signed correctly and will only work with 3.55 CFW. This package has been resigned and will work with all CFW versions as of Rogero/Rebug/Cobra 4.30
